Attributes.AttributeValues: The Bosch offering in sanding and polishing addresses finish requirements for wood, metal, paint removal and more. Whether the job calls for a belt sander, orbital sander, polisher or new multi-tool, Bosch has the right fit for the finish. Bi-directional sanding belts feature butt-splice construction for smooth running in both directions on belt sander. Designed for superior performance on wood, metal, plastic, fiberglass and other materials. Open-coat aluminum oxide abrasive resists loading for high removal rates and a great finish. Double-resin bonding and x-weight backings provide durability and longer belt life. Anti-static backing for highest removal and consistent finish. Contains a pack of 3 belts.

Save up to 60 percent on your water heating cost with an Eco Smart electric tank less water heater. Eco Smart tank less water heaters have standard, reliable, easily serviceable elements and heat exchangers that provide 99.8 percent. energy efficiency. Digital temperature control allows you to set your temperature in increments of 1 degree

EcoSmart Electric tankless water heaters, also called Instantaneous on demand water heaters, provide endless hot water on demand and only as needed. Self-modulating flow sensor technology regulates the amount of energy required to heat the water needed. This smart technology electric tankless water heater is configured for climates where incoming water temperature is 62 degree Fahrenheit and above. The ECO 18 is capable of heating over 2.5 GPM, which is the equivalent of one shower head (with a 1.5 GPM flow) and one sink with a low inlet water temperature of 62 degree Fahrenheit. Two showers can be run simultaneously when incoming water temperature is above 70 degree Fahrenheit in warmer climates such as South Texas, South Florida, New Mexico, Arizona and South California.
